<ab>Wir, die <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> dez <expan>r<ex>ats</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>st<ex>at</ex></expan> czü <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>bekenne<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>offenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> mit <expan>dis<ex>em</ex></expan> briefe
                        umb sölich ladung und klage, als Conrat
                            <expan>Reickershof<ex>er</ex></expan> czü Tanhawsen unsere güte geladen
                        hat auf die <expan>lantschran<ex>n</ex></expan> czü Hirsperg, daz wir <expan cert="unknown">H.</expan> Stainer, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, und <expan>C<ex>onrad</ex></expan>
<expan>Pilsach<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gancze<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt,
                        das an <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stat czü
                            <expan>verantwurt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und czü
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>tret<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, czügewinne und czü
                        verlust und czü <expan>alle<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Mit <expan>urk<ex>unde</ex></expan>
<expan>at<ex>er</ex>go</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Galli anno
                            ix<hi rend="sup">o</hi>. </ab>
